item.description:
Join Planned Parenthood League of Massachusetts (PPLM) for a “Party in the Plaza” in Davis Square on Saturday, October 3rd from 11:00am to 4:00pm. Enjoy free food, sexual health trivia, giveaways and more. Take advantage of our October promotion and get 3 months of birth control pills for $30 at PPLM's Express Center in the Plaza!


Host: Planned Parenthood League of Massachusetts
Date: Saturday October 3, 2009
Time: 11:00am – 4:00pm
Location: Plan: A Planned Parenthood Express Center
260 Elm Street, Davis Square Plaza
Somerville, MA 02144
item.name: Party in the Plaza!
